ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this course to a fellow student interested in Soviet Literature. I think the readings and discussion would be engaging for most students with such an interest.

The course provided a good introduction to an interesting period in Russian Literature and culture. The range of materials was diverse and all of them were very enjoyable. The class was lively and friendly. I would certainly recommend it to other students.
I woudl recommend it to anyone interested in in-depth study of Russian literature and with the reading knowledge of Russian.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course covered many areas of interest for me and gave me some very good ideas for further research.
